WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-ES

00:00:00.066 --> 00:00:02.950
Forms of runes, inscriptions.

00:00:02.950 --> 00:00:05.800
They are the work of my entire life.

00:00:05.800 --> 00:00:08.350
The more I study, the more I begin to see

00:00:08.350 --> 00:00:11.350
similar shapes in the stars.

00:00:11.800 --> 00:00:15.350
At that moment I decided to
focus on becoming

00:00:15.916 --> 00:00:17.233
a Rune Seeker.

00:00:18.550 --> 00:00:23.150
As Farrow has explained, runes
are very powerful and ancient inscriptions,

00:00:23.150 --> 00:00:26.350
and you can set them in your objects
to give them more power.

00:00:26.900 --> 00:00:30.300
During the league, inscribing symbols
on remnants will allow you to choose

00:00:30.300 --> 00:00:33.983
from several different crafting runes
to enhance your items.

00:00:34.633 --> 00:00:38.183
When you find a remnant,
it will have between two

00:00:38.733 --> 00:00:39.866
and seven spaces.

00:00:39.866 --> 00:00:42.783
More spaces mean a more powerful
encounter,

00:00:42.783 --> 00:00:45.450
but also
more options to choose from.

00:00:45.450 --> 00:00:47.333
At the beginning of the game, you
may find yourself

00:00:47.333 --> 00:00:49.400
crafting simple damage or resistance runes,

00:00:49.750 --> 00:00:51.116
which are available at lower levels

00:00:51.116 --> 00:00:52.616
than you would normally find them,

00:00:52.700 --> 00:00:54.433
and which will mean a decent power boost.

00:00:54.650 --> 00:00:56.516
But things improve quickly.

00:00:57.250 --> 00:01:00.233
There are 22 runes to add
or modify runic barrier,

00:01:00.483 --> 00:01:02.450
a new resource that can
protect you from death.

00:01:03.033 --> 00:01:06.900
With these runes, you can add
extra defense or turn your rune barrier

00:01:06.900 --> 00:01:10.150
into an offensive weapon using
Kalguran rune skills.

00:01:13.183 --> 00:01:16.600
There are also 13 runes that add
specific powers to certain types of weapons,

00:01:16.800 --> 00:01:19.833
like this one, which grants a chance
for grenades to explode a second time.

00:01:21.283 --> 00:01:24.566
Or this one that gives you a beneficial effect
called Druidic Feat

00:01:24.616 --> 00:01:26.200
when you completely stun enemies.

00:01:28.950 --> 00:01:29.850
In addition,

00:01:29.850 --> 00:01:32.850
there are 22 runes designed to give power
at low levels,

00:01:32.850 --> 00:01:35.850
like this one, which gives elemental resistances,

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:38.683
or this one, which gives a lot of spirit.

00:01:38.683 --> 00:01:42.300
These runes are designed to be powerful,
but they lose value at higher levels.

00:01:42.300 --> 00:01:45.300
They're great for quickly leveling up
a second character in the league.  We

00:01:45.733 --> 00:01:47.933
also have six runes that
can be used to expand

00:01:47.933 --> 00:01:51.016
the list of modifiers used
during high-level crafting.

00:01:51.600 --> 00:01:55.133
For example, you can socket
Katla's Melancholy into gloves

00:01:55.133 --> 00:01:58.516
and that will enable the crafting
of mods.  new decay items

00:01:58.600 --> 00:02:00.650
that you can use for
degenerative damage builds.

00:02:01.216 --> 00:02:03.316
After socketing one
of these runes,

00:02:03.316 --> 00:02:06.416
use exalted or chaos orbs
to try to obtain the mods.  new.

00:02:08.666 --> 00:02:10.583
There are several runes that have powerful

00:02:10.583 --> 00:02:13.900
and unique effects on objects,
but they remain linked forever.

00:02:14.066 --> 00:02:17.183
Like this one, which allows
any object to gain another suffix.

00:02:21.200 --> 00:02:23.516
Or this one, which allows you to create a setting for jewelry.

00:02:29.166 --> 00:02:30.400
Or this series of runes

00:02:30.400 --> 00:02:33.566
that can convert any
mod.  elemental from one element to another.

00:02:34.933 --> 00:02:37.700
There's even a rune that can
enhance any other rune,

00:02:37.700 --> 00:02:39.750
allowing you to improve the item
beyond normal.

00:02:42.133 --> 00:02:45.133
The last one I want to show is Legacy of Aldur,

00:02:45.433 --> 00:02:50.266
a special rune that you can socket into
unique Kalgurans or Ezomites to destroy them

00:02:50.266 --> 00:02:53.233
and create a new rune that has
some of the unique's properties.

00:02:53.816 --> 00:02:54.983
For example,

00:02:54.983 --> 00:02:58.350
use it in Fingercrusher to create
Fingercrusher Legacy.

00:02:58.500 --> 00:02:59.950
Attach it to boots and,

00:02:59.950 --> 00:03:01.683
just like the one they came from,

00:03:01.683 --> 00:03:05.233
you'll inflict 10% of the excess damage to
all enemies within two meters.

00:03:05.983 --> 00:03:08.700
Or how about Twisted Empyrean Legacy?

00:03:08.700 --> 00:03:10.466
Destroy a twisted Empyrean

00:03:10.466 --> 00:03:13.666
and you can add ice damage based
on your maximum mana to any weapon.

00:03:14.783 --> 00:03:17.900
With Aldur's Legacy, you can
create approximately one hundred more runes

00:03:17.900 --> 00:03:19.950
with all kinds of unique effects.

00:03:22.516 --> 00:03:25.116
At this point, you may think
that's a lot of runes,

00:03:25.116 --> 00:03:26.350
and you're right.

00:03:26.350 --> 00:03:28.350
This is Runes of Aldur,
after all.

00:03:28.350 --> 00:03:31.000
But we didn't want the
old runes to be left behind.

00:03:31.000 --> 00:03:32.700
A large number of old,

00:03:32.700 --> 00:03:34.800
unused runes have been improved,

00:03:34.800 --> 00:03:37.233
significantly enhancing
this crafting system.

00:03:37.566 --> 00:03:39.183
Explore everything the
runes have to offer

00:03:39.183 --> 00:03:42.883
in Return of the Ancients on May 29.
See you there!

